title: REDMI 9i Sport (Metallic Blue, 64 GB)  (4 GB RAM)

product_specification.In The Box: Handset, Power Adapter, Micro USB Cable, SIM Insertion Tool, Warranty Card, User Guide
product_specification.Operating Frequency: 2G GSM: B2, B3, B5, B8, 3G WCDMA: B1, B5, B8, 4G LTE TDD: B40, B41, 4G LTE FDD: B1, B3, B5, B8
product_specification.Primary Camera Features: 13MP Rear Camera Setup (f/2.2, 1.0μm Pixel Size, PDAF), HDR, Portrait, AI Scene Detection, Kaleidoscope, Filters, Pro Mode
product_specification.Secondary Camera Features: 5MP Front Camera (f/2.2, 1.12μm Pixel Size), Portrait, HDR, Portrait, Plam Shutter, Screen Flash, Beauty Mode
product_specification.Warranty Summary: Brand Warranty of 1 Year Available for Mobile and 6 Months for Accessories

product_description.Immersive Display: Enjoy watching videos and plunge yourself into a world of entertainment with the Redmi 9i Sport’s 16.58-cm (6.53) big HD+ IPS display, which delivers rich details and vivid colours.
product_description.Effortless Multitasking: Check your social media, play a game, and do much more simultaneously, thanks to the smooth performance and efficiency provided by 4 GB of RAM.
product_description.Game On!: Powered by the high-performance Helio G25 processor that delivers enhanced connectivity and sustained gaming, along with the HyperGame Engines technology, the Redmi 9i Sport ensures that you have all you need to defeat your virtual rivals.
product_description.Big on Battery Life: Listen to music, make calls, watch videos, play games, and do more without worrying about your phone dying out on you. Featuring a massive 5000 mAh high-capacity battery, the Redmi 9i Sport is ready to take on your everyday tasks like a champ.
product_description.Picture Perfect, Every Time: Make every photo you click a great shot with the 13 MP rear camera that is enhanced is AI Scene Detection technology.
product_description.Up Your Selfie Game: Take Instagram-worthy selfies every time with the 5 MP AI selfie camera.
product_description.Aura 360 Design: Featuring an elegant design with concentric circles and added grip on the back, the Redmi 9i Sport is truly a thing of beauty.
product_description.Built to Last: Protected by P2i, the Redmi 9i Sport easily withstands accidental splashes. It also comes with rubberised seals which prevent water ingression. What’s more, it features 380 V surge protection and corrosion-proof ports.
